Ticket ID: 003
Priority: Medium  
Status: Resolved  
Category: Operating System / Configuration  

## Customer Issue
Customer reports inability to join a Windows workstation to a domain. Domain and workgroup options are not visible in system settings.

## Environment
- OS: Windows 10 Home
- Network Type: NAT
- Device Type: Virtual Machine

## Steps to Reproduce
1. Open System Properties
2. Navigate to Computer Name settings
3. Attempt to locate Domain or Workgroup options
4. Options are not present

## Troubleshooting Performed
- Verified network connectivity
- Checked Windows edition
- Attempted to access `sysdm.cpl`
- Reviewed Microsoft documentation

## Root Cause Analysis
Windows 10 Home does not support domain join functionality.

## Resolution
Recommended upgrade to Windows 10 Pro to enable domain membership features.

## Customer Communication
Explained Windows edition limitations and provided guidance on upgrading.

## Time to Resolution
30 minutes